=head2 v5.17 January 21, 1996 by Andreas Koenig and Charles Bailey

Included a big patch by Charles Bailey for mksymlists(). This patch
intruduces a Mksymlists.pm file.

Included a patch by Roderick Schertler for Liblist.pm for DGUX.

Added PREFIX to PASTHRU (requested by Ilya).

Added a C<-E<gt>>depend method in the MM_Unix package that acts just
like the macro method and lets the user add any dependency
